OL,4,G1935FDanger Man
OL,5,     GJohn Drake visits the tiny nation
OL,6,     Gof San Pablo to investigate an
OL,7,     Gapparent suicide. The victim,
OL,8,     GWinfield, was a US treasury
OL,9,     Grepresentative with a reputation
OL,10,     Gfor spending lavishly on women
OL,11,     Gand gambling.
OL,12,G2005FHallelujah!
OL,13,     GCaptain Emily Ridley has been
OL,14,     Gasked to retire from her position
OL,15,     Gin the Salvation Army but she
OL,16,     Grefuses. Now the Army must decide
OL,17,     Gwhat to do with this overbearing
OL,18,     Gwoman who relentlessly targets
OL,19,     Gsinners.
